StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCity]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @StateCode varchar(3), @CountyCode varchar(4), @CityCode varchar(5) ) AS
SELECT ID, Code, [Name], CountyCode, CountyName, StateCode, StateName FROM [USMC].[vwCi.es] WHERE StateCode = @StateCode AND CountyCode = @CountyCode AND Code = @CityCode AND [Name] IS NOT NULL ORDER BY [Name]
